<template>
    <StaticMapWithMarkers
  :center="{ lat: 35.6892, lon: 51.3890 }"
  :markers="markers"
/>

</template>
<script setup>
  import StaticMapWithMarkers from '@/components/tooles/places/StaticMapWithMarkers.vue';
  import { usePlaceStore } from '@/stores/place';
  import { onMounted } from 'vue';
  onMounted(()=>{
    usePlaceStore.fetchAllPlaces()
  })
  const markers = [
  {
    lat: 35.6892,
    lon: 51.3890,
    title: 'نقطه اول',
    description: 'توضیح کوتاه درباره این نقطه',
    medias: ['https://example.com/image1.jpg']
  },
  {
    lat: 35.7,
    lon: 51.4,
    title: 'نقطه دوم',
    description: 'توضیح دیگر...',
    medias: []
  }
]

</script>
